conjure-up (0.1.0) xenial-proposed; urgency=medium

  * Change name from conjure to conjure-up
  * Use daily stream for importing LXD images in Juju
  * Update bundle editor to include better navigation between
    relation editing and charm addition
  * Bundle editor will not show recommendedCharms if charm exists
    in current bundle.
  * Facilitates configuring LXD bridge through its dpkg-reconfigure lxd
    mechanism and handles bringing up lxdbr0 for Juju to consume
  * Implemented caching for application config for subsequent status runs

 -- Adam Stokes <adam.stokes@ubuntu.com>  Thu, 14 Apr 2016 16:03:54 -0400

